Plan for this work:


Installed napalm and it's requirements:
pip3 install napalm
sudo apt-get install -y --force-yes libssl-


Router_commands:
no ip domain-lookup
username mea priv 15 pass cisco
ip domain-name tsm
ip ssh ver 2
crypto key generate rsa general-keys modulus 1024 
line vty 0 4
trans in ssh
login local
line aux 0
transport preferred none
exec-timeout 15 0
int fa0/0
ip add dhcp
no shut

DHCP_Server:
ip dhcp excluded-address 10.10.10.0 10.10.10.10
ip dhcp pool CourseDHCP
network 10.10.10.0 255.255.255.0
default-router 10.10.10.2
dns-server 10.10.10.2
int fa0/0 
ip add 10.10.10.1 255.255.255.0  
no shut 


